lead_paragraph: Gary Woodland birdied three of the final four holes Friday for a 6-under 65 and a one-stroke lead in the PGA Tour's OHL Classic at Mayakoba.

headline.print_headline: Gary Woodland Shoots 65, Leads OHL Classic at Mayakoba
